    20Ôćĺ## Benefits over plain `fetch`
    22Ôćĺ- Simpler API
    23Ôćĺ- Method shortcuts (`ky.post()`)
    24Ôćĺ- Treats non-2xx status codes as errors (after redirects)
    25Ôćĺ- Retries failed requests
    26Ôćĺ- JSON option
    27Ôćĺ- Timeout support
    28Ôćĺ- URL prefix option
    29Ôćĺ- Instances with custom defaults
    30Ôćĺ- Hooks
